{
  "stem": "1062.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Need a mic, too, huh?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this town, Comlausa, you're not going to find it on any map.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a small village, which consisted of 26 Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe the entire village, maybe were about 200, maybe, families all together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of them were Romanian people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My family-- we were eight in my immediate family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My-- my parents-- mother, father-- and I had four brothers and a sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was born in 1928.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, this village was part of Romania.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The-- the village had one old schoolhouse, which was rebuilt in the mid-'30s.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember going to the old one and also to the new one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But most of our-- the emphasis was not put on-- on-- on secular education.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The emphasis was put more on the Yiddish education.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In other words, we had a cheder there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And even so we were only 26 families, my village always prided itself of having one of the best cheders for the entire area.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there were villages which are much larger than my village.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They would send their children to my village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had two cheders.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One cheder was [HEBREW] Melamed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This Melamed, his name was Reb Moishele.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was a small fellow, and he hardly made a living.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they would pay, it was called [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They would pay so much for a season to send the children there to-- to study.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I believe we started-- when you were 3 years old, you know, they used to shave off your head.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then you had Peahs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they went to the-- they went to cheder, to Moishele.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Moishele, and his wife's name was [?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
